text:
the professor responded to my email: 
Hello,

For longer questions such as these, it is better if you come to my office
hours.

Briefly:
1. There are no dedicated resources available for this course. I am not aware
of non-course specific resources (apart from your ENCS) you could use as a
student. I usually recommend to use some cloud computing resources, such as
Amazon's EC2 free tier, for setting up a demo.

2. I cannot find the student you mentioned (Mofehintoluwa Ogunrinde) in the
class list, so most likely he dropped the course. However, before you remove
him from your project, please notify the TA and also make sure you document
the past (non-)contributions from him.

Regards,

Ren√© Witte
The TA said that he wants us to remove his name from the github
